					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="text-align: center;"> <blockquote> <p><span style="font-style: italic;"><a href="https://youtu.be/nDcD62i0MpI" target="_blank">My infiltrated mind</a><br /> <a href="https://youtu.be/nDcD62i0MpI" target="_blank">My lacerated soul</a><br /> <a href="https://youtu.be/nDcD62i0MpI" target="_blank">It took me years, create me, control you</a><br /> <a href="https://youtu.be/nDcD62i0MpI" target="_blank">I left myself for an idea I stole</a></span></p> </blockquote> </div> <blockquote> <p><strong>Buggy Hardware (or Why I Don't Play Violent Video Games)</strong><br /> <strong>Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580931977" alt="Lt Flops" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" >Lt Flops</a></span></p> </blockquote> <hr /> <p>This is my entry for <strong>Round 2</strong> of the <strong><a target="_blank" href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-oct-hub">SCP Original Character Tournament</a></strong>! I was matched up against <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2005044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580931977" alt="Decibelles" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2005044)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" >Decibelles</a></span>' character (<strong><a target="_blank" href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-3090">Heather Mason</a></strong>) and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kinchtheknifeblade" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1345012&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580931977" alt="kinchtheknifeblade" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1345012)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kinchtheknifeblade" >kinchtheknifeblade</a></span>'s character (<strong><a target="_blank" href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-2852">Cousin Johnny</a></strong>). The competing Tale is as follows:</p> <blockquote> <p><sub><strong><a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/sometimes-manna-is-just-a-cicada-shell">Sometimes Manna Is Just a Cicada Shell</a></strong> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kinchtheknifeblade" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1345012&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580931977" alt="kinchtheknifeblade" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1345012)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kinchtheknifeblade" >kinchtheknifeblade</a></span></sub></p> </blockquote> <p>▶ <strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/a-scene-from-a-meme" target="_blank">Part 3</a></strong></p> <hr /> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▶&nbsp;Special&nbsp;Thanks</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:110%;"><strong>Special Thanks &#8212; Lovely Critters</strong></span></p> <p>▶ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yossipossi" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2199269&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1580931977" alt="Yossipossi" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2199269)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yossipossi" >Yossipossi</a></span><br /> ▶ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=158